acking detectors, in terms of\ntracking efficiency, space resolution, count rate capability and momenta\nresolution. The current prototype, which is the generation four of this type,\nis two GEM-TPCs in twin configuration inside the same vessel. This means that\none of the GEM-TPC is flipped on the middle plane w.r.t. the other one. This\nchamber was tested at Jyv\\\"askyl\\\"a accelerator with protons projectiles and at\nGSI with Uranium, fragments and Carbon beams during this year 2016.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Nov 2017 07:38:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-03"}
