et in SU$_f$(3). The tetraquark mixing\nframework including the flavor mixing is tested for the isoscalar resonances in\nterms of the mass splitting and the fall-apart decay modes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Nov 2017 10:31:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 14 Feb 2018 02:02:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-16"}
