riod and ten in magnetic moment. The\nparameter-dependence and normalisation constant that we determine are in\nagreement with basic accretion theory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Nov 2017 11:26:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-28"}
