ormulation\nnumerically shows improved energy behavior for turbulent flows comparing with\nthe original VMS method.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Nov 2017 15:33:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 2 Oct 2018 12:55:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-03"}
